    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game by Аnatoliy Loginovskikh</h2><br><strong>This is the first 3D game in the &quot;100 hidden objects&quot; series.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Important information</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Press &quot;Del&quot; then &quot;Exit&quot; to RESET ALL ACHIEVEMENT and restart the game. <br>It is recommended to restart Steam Client after resetting achievements.<br></li><li>You can use the mouse or &quot;WASD&quot; to move around the location.<br></li><li>The game has automatic saves associated with achievements.<br></li><li>If you have continued the game, please wait until the frogs (score) have loaded.</li></ul><br>100 hidden frogs 2 is a hidden object game in the magic medieval setting.<br>Colorful 3D graphics. A level that can be viewed from all sides.<br>It's a fun but challenging adventure.<br><br>Can you find 100 frogs? Just click on the frog!<br>Take care of your nerves!",
